{"type":null,"faqId":18046,"title":"荣耀3C 4G版 Emui3.0为什么拍摄夜晚的景色，即使使用了闪光灯，画面还是不亮？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">手机上后置led补光灯的亮度是有限的，所以对于远处的夜景，即使使用闪光灯拍照也是无法照亮整个场景的。另外使用闪光灯时也要注意您的手指或者其他手机上的装饰件不要遮挡到光线，否则也会造成拍出的画面不清晰。<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"800","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420450037000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":53,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C,4G版,EMUI3.0,3.0,照片,景色,闪光灯","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}